The Evil Within 2 (c) Bethesda Softworks

Release Date :  10/2017              Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Violent

From mastermind Shinji Mikami,  The Evil  Within 2  is  the  latest
evolution of survival horror. Detective Sebastian  Castellanos  has
lost it all. But when given a chance to save his daughter,  he must
descend once more into the nightmarish world  of  STEM.  Horrifying
threats emerge from every  corner as  the world  twists  and  warps
around him. Will Sebastian face adversity head on with  weapons and
traps, or sneak through the shadows to survive
